com.rfid

类 ReaderDataPackageProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.module.interaction.DataPackageProcess
        • com.rfid.ReaderDataPackageProcess

  • public class ReaderDataPackageProcess
extends DataPackageProcess
    The implementation class of DataPackageProcess.You can process the data package return by RFID reader.And DataPackageProcess is an #Observable,it will send data package to #RXObserver.So the client can receive the processed data by override the according method in #RXObserver.Before you must register it to #RFIDReaderHelper subclass.
